title: Ra Sushi and Bar
typeOfFood: Ovo, Japanese, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Asian, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Sushi restaurant with a local focus and uses ingredients from nearby areas. Offers veggie maki, nigri, and a vegan set menu called "no fish olsen." Not wheelchair accessible because there is a stair with 16 steps into the eating area. If you explain your diet issues staff can make something for you. Has gluten-free soy sauce. Reservation not necessary but recommended on weekends. Also an outlet in the shopping mall Nerstranda.
